{"id":"2997376a-8ae8-4b74-804c-abc37a64907c","title":"1549/06/08: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"7c9f5e44-d091-46e0-84a0-dab83c65e576","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [June 8th, 1549].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"ea900fbf-764c-4824-bf7d-357d7d182e81","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"86324348-e80c-4c92-ba0b-96d3411438d2","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c56ce966-e6e8-4635-ae22-b2a9a4c8aa4c","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":25,"value":"1a868f85-bf0a-4668-be6c-6595e22992d3","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"470d3b98-b9f8-432d-851e-f49a3f938242","type":"style/superscript","start":18,"end":19,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bc9bc928-d3f6-4f6e-a9c2-9daacde62ae2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"a8cf2203-103c-404f-a40a-8b43088ec7ab","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0d8e2327-28ec-4785-af5e-56a79dc29f65","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"54cf54c9-1ead-4c16-bc7f-423634879430","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6895a78e-217b-499d-a610-e0784416f17c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2f50ad28-40f2-4dd9-9dc3-bc013ac1dedb","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a3954210-047c-4a28-920d-5f4830f52cf6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"be38b73f-7579-43db-aa4d-936428936a76","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0With regard to the farm at Monte Spertoli, it seems to me dishonest that they should ask four hundred crowns more than it is worth. It rather looks as if ye had appeared too eager about it and that they had put up the price on that account.\u00A0I do not think they would find a purchaser anywhere\u00A0else for it at so much more than it is worth. If it were a question of fifty or a hundred crowns I should not mind so much: however, I leave it in your hands, and if ye think well to take it, do so, for whatever ye may do will be well done. I have not been able to draw up the power of attorney for I can decipher so little of thy letter that I get an attack of fever every time I attempt to read it. I will try to draw it up during the coming week if I can make out what is required of me. I have received the Trebbiano: the little bundle (fardelletto) mentioned in thy letter has not yet arrived. As to my illness, I am much better compared with what I was before. For about two months past I have had to drink, every morning and evening, a certain sort of water which breaks up the\u00A0stone. It is obtained from a spring about forty miles from Rome. It has broken mine and enabled me to pass water with tolerable ease. I shall have to store up a supply of it in the house and use nothing else either for drinking or cooking: and I shall have to alter my mode of life.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"da8efcd2-aa83-4022-b7d3-7bb69c6a5b39","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a7017dd1-7d52-40df-ae85-963d739fec51","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4488067c-5bf4-4015-b8fe-0fe5cecfc21f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":31,"end":34,"value":"1281fb56-a1f0-43a